  <name>Acquacotta</name>
  <summary>Pomodoro time tracking application</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Acquacotta is a Pomodoro time tracking application that helps you stay
      focused and productive. Track your work sessions with customizable timers,
      categorize your work by type, and view detailed reports of your productivity.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Configurable work and break durations</li>
      <li>Pause and resume timer functionality</li>
      <li>Categorize pomodoros by type (Product, Content, Team, etc.)</li>
      <li>View daily, weekly, and monthly reports with charts</li>
      <li>Export data to CSV</li>
      <li>Desktop notifications with sound alerts</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
